---
layout: base.njk
title: Insights
description: Writing on HR analytics, measurement, prediction, and decision-making under uncertainty.
---

<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <div class="section-label">Insights</div>
    <h1>Thinking out loud about measurement, prediction, and people.</h1>
    <p class="page-intro">Writing on what good HR analytics looks like — and what it usually doesn't.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="insights-list">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    {% if collections.posts.length %}
      {% for post in collections.posts %}
      <article class="post-preview post-preview--full">
        <time class="post-date">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</time>
        <h2><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h2>
        {% if post.data.excerpt %}<p>{{ post.data.excerpt }}</p>{% endif %}
        <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="read-more">Read &rarr;</a>
      </article>
      {% endfor %}
    {% else %}
      <p class="empty-state">No posts yet — check back soon.</p>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
</section>
